original_title: A Gay In The Life of A Superhero: The Making of the Fagatron 2022 Calendar
overview: Enter the world of fashion visionary FAGATRON. Go behind the scenes of the making of the Fagatron 2022 Calendar as captured by the lens of Avant Garde artist Chad Hughes. Forget everything you know about being the King of Galaxia. Take a trip inside A Gay In The Life Of A Superhero.
title: A Gay In The Life of A Superhero: The Making of the Fagatron 2022 Calendar
